WEBVTT

00:00.250 --> 00:05.000
Karl likes to spend time with his grandmother 
 when he has some free time in the evening.

00:05.083 --> 00:09.750
One day he was talking to her about 
 what he would work in the future.

00:10.250 --> 00:12.750
The grandmother then began to cry

00:12.750 --> 00:17.417
and told him about his grandfather 
 who had worked in coal mining

00:17.583 --> 00:21.583
and had died in an accident many years ago.

00:21.917 --> 00:24.250
The grandmother spoke:

00:24.250 --> 00:28.250
"I wish that you will have a less 
 life-threatening job."
